Package: exim.gov
Title: Export-Import Bank of the US Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for Export-Import Bank authorization data. Search, filter, and
    summarize EXIM Bank deals by country, year, and program. Includes LLM context injection via exim_context().
